# Project Structure Reference

This file provides a quick reference to the project structure.

## Core Directories

- `data/` - Data directories (contents gitignored)
- `evidence/` - Source evidence documents (organized by type)
- `filings/` - Administrative filing materials
- `research/` - Research and analysis outputs
- `scripts/` - Analysis scripts (organized by function)
- `docs/` - Documentation (guides and reference)
- `outputs/` - Generated outputs (reports and summaries)

## Key Files

- `README.md` - Main project documentation
- `organize_evidence.R` - Master organization script
- `requirements.txt` - Python dependencies
- `state_dpor_registry.csv` - State registry

## Script Organization

- `scripts/extraction/` - Evidence extraction scripts
- `scripts/search/` - Search and discovery scripts
- `scripts/analysis/` - Analysis scripts
- `scripts/legacy/` - Deprecated scripts

## Documentation Organization

- `docs/guides/` - User guides
- `docs/reference/` - Reference materials
- `docs/INDEX.md` - Documentation index
- `docs/MAINTENANCE_GUIDE.md` - Maintenance guide

## Output Organization

- `outputs/reports/` - Generated HTML reports
- `outputs/summaries/` - Summary CSV files
